author: Solid jj
description:
After the events of the Cell Game, Gohan, Piccolo, Krillin, Tien and that other guy gather to try and wish for Goku to return. However, can they fulfill their wish? Does Goku even want to come back? Did he know about Goten because that's never really explored? Find out on this 3 minute episode of Dragon Ball Z!
